            <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" resp="#AA">
                <p>Stateios Eutyches, lived blamelessly for 16 years, 3 months, 7 days.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>It is unclear why Kaibel states that Torremuzza's edition (1784) is derivative from Ferrara (1829).</p>
            </div>
